      • with

        public <DataT,InputT,OutputT> CombineFns.ComposedCombineFn<DataT> with(SimpleFunction<DataT,InputT> extractInputFn,
                                                                       Combine.CombineFn<InputT,?,OutputT> combineFn,
                                                                       TupleTag<OutputT> outputTag)
        Returns a CombineFns.ComposedCombineFn that can take additional GlobalCombineFns and apply them as a single combine function.

        The CombineFns.ComposedCombineFn extracts inputs from DataT with the extractInputFn and combines them with the combineFn, and then it outputs each combined value with a TupleTag to a CombineFns.CoCombineResult.

      • with

        public <DataT,InputT,OutputT> CombineFns.ComposedCombineFnWithContext<DataT> with(SimpleFunction<DataT,InputT> extractInputFn,

        Returns a CombineFns.ComposedCombineFnWithContext that can take additional GlobalCombineFns and apply them as a single combine function.

        The CombineFns.ComposedCombineFnWithContext extracts inputs from DataT with the extractInputFn and combines them with the combineFnWithContext, and then it outputs each combined value with a TupleTag to a CombineFns.CoCombineResult.
